Nodejitsu,is,a,cloud,hosting,platform,as,a,service,for,node,js,developers,The,platform,lets,developers,host,and,scale,their,applications,offers,a,marketplace,for,node,js,applications,and,lets,developers,get,training,The,API,lets,developers,interact,with,the,Nodejitsu,platform,programatically,It,exposes,data,on,applications,users,databases,and,more,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON